   {
    "narration": "各位羽翼，你们能听到吗@我是梓美冬",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-4"
   },
   {
    "narration": "我决定脱离玛吉斯之翼",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-5",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-4"
   },
   {
    "narration": "我觉得不能再服从她们了@被施加过[textBlue:传闻]的羽翼们@应该都能明白这一点",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-6",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-5"
   },
   {
    "narration": "我早该在各位受到伤害前@阻止这一切就好了@但因为反抗后被关了起来@没来得及早点向大家传达",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-7",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101942/vo_full_101942-3-6"
